      "raw_text": "NJ. Eugene SkOrniakOff. special\nagent Of the department of agricul\nture of teh Russian empire, who Is\ncollecting data on government and\nprivate irrigation projects in the\nUnited States for the car, will be\nin Spokane some time next week\nto inspect the works in the Spo-\nkane valley, going from here to\nLewiston, and on his return to Spo-\nkane he will visit the projects in\nthe Yakima and Wenatchee val\nleys, also points in Oregon. He\nwill represent Russia at the seven\nteenth session of the National Irri-\ncation congress in Spokane, Aug.\n8 to IA."
